==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[i-]]'' (indeterminate [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-o]]'' (correlative suffix of objects)

===Correlative===
'''io''' (''plural'' '''[[ioj]]''', ''accusative singular'' '''[[ion]]''', ''accusative plural'' '''[[iojn]]''')

# [[something]] (indeterminate correlative of objects)
#: Like other indeterminate correlatives, '''io''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Io''' ajn'' thus means ''[[anything]]''.

[[Category:Esperanto correlatives]]
